{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Do you remember the story"},{"time":2000,"text":"of Odysseus and the Sirens"},{"time":4000,"text":"from high school or junior high school?"},{"time":6000,"text":"There was this hero, Odysseus, who's heading back home"},{"time":9000,"text":"after the Trojan War."},{"time":11000,"text":"And he's standing on the deck of his ship,"},{"time":13000,"text":"he's talking to his first mate,"},{"time":15000,"text":"and he's saying,"},{"time":17000,"text":"\"Tomorrow, we will sail past those rocks,"},{"time":20000,"text":"and on those rocks sit some beautiful women"},{"time":22000,"text":"called Sirens."},{"time":24000,"text":"And these women sing an enchanting song,"},{"time":27000,"text":"a song so alluring"},{"time":29000,"text":"that all sailors who hear it"},{"time":31000,"text":"crash into the rocks and die.\""},{"time":33000,"text":"Now you would expect, given that,"},{"time":35000,"text":"that they would choose an alternate route around the Sirens,"},{"time":38000,"text":"but instead Odysseus says,"},{"time":41000,"text":"\"I want to hear that song."},{"time":43000,"text":"And so what I'm going to do"},{"time":45000,"text":"is I'm going to pour wax in the ears"},{"time":47000,"text":"of you and all the men --"},{"time":49000,"text":"stay with me --"},{"time":51000,"text":"so that you can't hear the song,"},{"time":53000,"text":"and then I'm going to have you tie me to the mast"},{"time":56000,"text":"so that I can listen"},{"time":58000,"text":"and we can all sail by unaffected.\""},{"time":60000,"text":"So this is a captain"},{"time":63000,"text":"putting the life of every single person on the ship at risk"},{"time":65000,"text":"so that he can hear a song."}]},{"cues":[{"time":67000,"text":"And I'd like to think if this was the case,"},{"time":69000,"text":"they probably would have rehearsed it a few times."},{"time":72000,"text":"Odysseus would have said, \"Okay, let's do a dry run."},{"time":75000,"text":"You tie me to the mast, and I'm going to beg and plead."},{"time":78000,"text":"And no matter what I say, you cannot untie me from the mast."},{"time":80000,"text":"All right, so tie me to the mast.\""},{"time":82000,"text":"And the first mate takes a rope"},{"time":84000,"text":"and ties Odysseus to the mast in a nice knot."},{"time":87000,"text":"And Odysseus does his best job playacting"},{"time":89000,"text":"and says, \"Untie me. Untie me."},{"time":91000,"text":"I want to hear that song. Untie me.\""},{"time":93000,"text":"And the first mate wisely resists"},{"time":95000,"text":"and doesn't untie Odysseus."},{"time":97000,"text":"And then Odysseus says, \"I see that you can get it."},{"time":100000,"text":"All right, untie me now and we'll get some dinner.\""},{"time":103000,"text":"And the first mate hesitates."},{"time":105000,"text":"He's like, \"Is this still the rehearsal,"},{"time":107000,"text":"or should I untie him?\""},{"time":110000,"text":"And the first mate thinks,"},{"time":112000,"text":"\"Well, I guess at some point the rehearsal has to end.\""},{"time":115000,"text":"So he unties Odysseus, and Odysseus flips out."},{"time":118000,"text":"He's like, \"You idiot. You moron."},{"time":120000,"text":"If you do that tomorrow, I'll be dead, you'll be dead,"},{"time":122000,"text":"every single one of the men will be dead."},{"time":124000,"text":"Now just don't untie me no matter what.\""},{"time":127000,"text":"He throws the first mate to the ground."},{"time":129000,"text":"This repeats itself through the night --"},{"time":131000,"text":"rehearsal, tying to the mast,"},{"time":133000,"text":"conning his way out of it,"},{"time":135000,"text":"beating the poor first mate up mercilessly."},{"time":138000,"text":"Hilarity ensues."}]},{"cues":[{"time":141000,"text":"Tying yourself to a mast"},{"time":143000,"text":"is perhaps the oldest written example"},{"time":145000,"text":"of what psychologists call a commitment device."},{"time":148000,"text":"A commitment device is a decision that you make"},{"time":151000,"text":"with a cool head to bind yourself"},{"time":154000,"text":"so that you don't do something regrettable"},{"time":156000,"text":"when you have a hot head."},{"time":159000,"text":"Because there's two heads inside one person"},{"time":161000,"text":"when you think about it."},{"time":163000,"text":"Scholars have long invoked this metaphor of two selves"},{"time":166000,"text":"when it comes to questions of temptation."},{"time":169000,"text":"There is first, the present self."},{"time":172000,"text":"This is like Odysseus when he's hearing the song."},{"time":175000,"text":"He just wants to get to the front row."},{"time":177000,"text":"He just thinks about the here and now and the immediate gratification."},{"time":180000,"text":"But then there's this other self, the future self."},{"time":183000,"text":"This is Odysseus as an old man"},{"time":185000,"text":"who wants nothing more than to retire in a sunny villa"},{"time":188000,"text":"with his wife Penelope"},{"time":190000,"text":"outside of Ithaca -- the other one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":196000,"text":"So why do we need commitment devices?"},{"time":200000,"text":"Well resisting temptation is hard,"},{"time":202000,"text":"as the 19th century English economist"},{"time":205000,"text":"Nassau William Senior said,"},{"time":207000,"text":"\"To abstain from the enjoyment which is in our power,"},{"time":210000,"text":"or to seek distant rather than immediate results,"},{"time":213000,"text":"are among the most painful exertions"},{"time":215000,"text":"of the human will.\""},{"time":217000,"text":"If you set goals for yourself and you're like a lot of other people,"},{"time":220000,"text":"you probably realize"},{"time":222000,"text":"it's not that your goals are physically impossible"},{"time":224000,"text":"that's keeping you from achieving them,"},{"time":226000,"text":"it's that you lack the self-discipline to stick to them."},{"time":229000,"text":"It's physically possible to lose weight."},{"time":231000,"text":"It's physically possible to exercise more."},{"time":234000,"text":"But resisting temptation"},{"time":236000,"text":"is hard."}]},{"cues":[{"time":238000,"text":"The other reason"},{"time":240000,"text":"that it's difficult to resist temptation"},{"time":243000,"text":"is because it's an unequal battle"},{"time":246000,"text":"between the present self and the future self."},{"time":248000,"text":"I mean, let's face it, the present self is present."},{"time":250000,"text":"It's in control. It's in power right now."},{"time":253000,"text":"It has these strong, heroic arms"},{"time":255000,"text":"that can lift doughnuts into your mouth."},{"time":257000,"text":"And the future self is not even around."},{"time":260000,"text":"It's off in the future. It's weak."},{"time":263000,"text":"It doesn't even have a lawyer present."},{"time":265000,"text":"There's nobody to stick up for the future self."},{"time":267000,"text":"And so the present self can trounce"},{"time":270000,"text":"all over its dreams."},{"time":272000,"text":"So there's this battle between the two selves that's being fought,"},{"time":276000,"text":"and we need commitment devices"},{"time":278000,"text":"to level the playing field between the two."}]},{"cues":[{"time":281000,"text":"Now I'm a big fan of commitment devices actually."},{"time":284000,"text":"Tying yourself to the mast is the oldest one, but there are other ones"},{"time":287000,"text":"such as locking a credit card away with a key"},{"time":291000,"text":"or not bringing junk food into the house so you won't eat it"},{"time":294000,"text":"or unplugging your Internet connection"},{"time":296000,"text":"so you can use your computer."},{"time":298000,"text":"I was creating commitment devices of my own"},{"time":300000,"text":"long before I knew what they were."},{"time":302000,"text":"So when I was a starving post-doc"},{"time":304000,"text":"at Columbia University,"},{"time":306000,"text":"I was deep in a publish-or-perish phase of my career."},{"time":309000,"text":"I had to write five pages a day"},{"time":311000,"text":"towards papers"},{"time":313000,"text":"or I would have to give up five dollars."}]},{"cues":[{"time":316000,"text":"And when you try to execute these commitment devices,"},{"time":319000,"text":"you realize the devil is really in the details."},{"time":321000,"text":"Because it's not that easy to get rid of five dollars."},{"time":324000,"text":"I mean, you can't burn it; that's illegal."},{"time":327000,"text":"And I thought, well I could give it to a charity"},{"time":329000,"text":"or give it to my wife or something like that."},{"time":331000,"text":"But then I thought, oh, I'm sending myself mixed messages."},{"time":333000,"text":"Because not writing is bad, but giving to charity is good."},{"time":336000,"text":"So then I would kind of justify not writing"},{"time":338000,"text":"by giving a gift."},{"time":340000,"text":"And then I kind of flipped that around and thought,"},{"time":342000,"text":"well I could give it to the neo-Nazis."},{"time":344000,"text":"But then I was like, that's more bad than writing is good,"},{"time":347000,"text":"and so that wouldn't work."},{"time":349000,"text":"So ultimately, I just decided"},{"time":351000,"text":"I would leave it in an envelope on the subway."},{"time":354000,"text":"Sometimes a good person would find it,"},{"time":356000,"text":"sometimes a bad person would find it."},{"time":358000,"text":"On average, it was just a completely pointless exchange of money"},{"time":361000,"text":"that I would regret."},{"time":363000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":366000,"text":"Such it is with commitment devices."}]},{"cues":[{"time":369000,"text":"But despite my like for them,"},{"time":373000,"text":"there's two nagging concerns"},{"time":375000,"text":"that I've always had about commitment devices,"},{"time":377000,"text":"and you might feel this if you use them yourself."},{"time":379000,"text":"So the first is,"},{"time":381000,"text":"when you've got one of these devices going,"},{"time":383000,"text":"such as this contract to write everyday or pay,"},{"time":386000,"text":"it's just a constant reminder"},{"time":388000,"text":"that you have no self-control."},{"time":390000,"text":"You're just telling yourself, \"Without you, commitment device,"},{"time":392000,"text":"I am nothing, I have no self-discipline.\""},{"time":395000,"text":"And then when you're ever in a situation"},{"time":397000,"text":"where you don't have a commitment device in place --"},{"time":400000,"text":"like, \"Oh my God, that person's offering me a doughnut,"},{"time":402000,"text":"and I have no defense mechanism,\" --"},{"time":404000,"text":"you just eat it."},{"time":406000,"text":"So I don't like the way that they take the power away from you."},{"time":409000,"text":"I think self-discipline is something, it's like a muscle."},{"time":412000,"text":"The more you exercise it, the stronger it gets."}]},{"cues":[{"time":415000,"text":"The other problem with commitment devices"},{"time":417000,"text":"is that you can always weasel your way out of them."},{"time":420000,"text":"You say, \"Well, of course I can't write today,"},{"time":422000,"text":"because I'm giving a TEDTalk and I have five media interviews,"},{"time":425000,"text":"and then I'm going to a cocktail party and then I'll be drunk after that."},{"time":428000,"text":"And so there's no way that this is going to work.\""},{"time":431000,"text":"So in effect, you are like Odysseus and the first mate"},{"time":433000,"text":"in one person."},{"time":435000,"text":"You're putting yourself, you're binding yourself,"},{"time":438000,"text":"and you're weaseling your way out of it,"},{"time":440000,"text":"and then you're beating yourself up afterwards."}]},{"cues":[{"time":442000,"text":"So I've been working"},{"time":444000,"text":"for about a decade now"},{"time":446000,"text":"on finding other ways"},{"time":448000,"text":"to change people's relationship to the future self"},{"time":450000,"text":"without using commitment devices."},{"time":452000,"text":"In particular, I'm interested in the relationship"},{"time":455000,"text":"to the future financial self."},{"time":459000,"text":"And this is a timely issue."},{"time":461000,"text":"I'm talking about the topic of saving."},{"time":463000,"text":"Now saving is a classic two selves problem."},{"time":465000,"text":"The present self does not want to save at all."},{"time":468000,"text":"It wants to consume."},{"time":470000,"text":"Whereas the future self wants the present self to save."},{"time":474000,"text":"So this is a timely problem."},{"time":476000,"text":"We look at the savings rate"},{"time":478000,"text":"and it has been declining since the 1950s."},{"time":481000,"text":"At the same time, the Retirement Risk Index,"},{"time":484000,"text":"the chance of not being able to meet your needs in retirement,"},{"time":487000,"text":"has been increasing."},{"time":489000,"text":"And we're at a situation now"},{"time":491000,"text":"where for every three baby boomers,"},{"time":493000,"text":"the McKinsey Global Institute predicts"},{"time":495000,"text":"that two will not be able to meet their pre-retirement needs"},{"time":499000,"text":"while they're in retirement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":501000,"text":"So what can we do about this?"},{"time":504000,"text":"There's a philosopher, Derek Parfit,"},{"time":507000,"text":"who said some words that were inspiring to my coauthors and I."},{"time":510000,"text":"He said that, \"We might neglect our future selves"},{"time":513000,"text":"because of some failure of belief or imagination.\""},{"time":517000,"text":"That is to say,"},{"time":519000,"text":"we somehow might not believe that we're going to get old,"},{"time":522000,"text":"or we might not be able to imagine"},{"time":524000,"text":"that we're going to get old some day."},{"time":526000,"text":"On the one hand, it sounds ridiculous."},{"time":528000,"text":"Of course, we know that we're going to get old."},{"time":530000,"text":"But aren't there things that we believe and don't believe at the same time?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":533000,"text":"So my coauthors and I have used computers,"},{"time":536000,"text":"the greatest tool of our time,"},{"time":538000,"text":"to assist people's imagination"},{"time":540000,"text":"and help them imagine what it might be like"},{"time":543000,"text":"to go into the future."},{"time":545000,"text":"And I'll show you some of these tools right here."},{"time":548000,"text":"The first is called the distribution builder."},{"time":550000,"text":"It shows people what the future might be like"},{"time":553000,"text":"by showing them a hundred equally probable outcomes"},{"time":556000,"text":"that might be obtained in the future."},{"time":558000,"text":"Each outcome is shown by one of these markers,"},{"time":561000,"text":"and each sits on a row"},{"time":563000,"text":"that represents a level of wealth and retirement."},{"time":565000,"text":"Being up at the top"},{"time":567000,"text":"means that you're enjoying a high income in retirement."},{"time":569000,"text":"Being down at the bottom"},{"time":571000,"text":"means that you're struggling to make ends meet."},{"time":573000,"text":"When you make an investment,"},{"time":575000,"text":"what you're really saying is, \"I accept"},{"time":577000,"text":"that any one of these 100 things"},{"time":579000,"text":"could happen to me and determine my wealth.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":581000,"text":"Now you can try to move your outcomes around."},{"time":584000,"text":"You can try to manipulate your fate, like this person is doing,"},{"time":587000,"text":"but it costs you something to do it."},{"time":589000,"text":"It means that you have to save more today."},{"time":593000,"text":"Once you find an investment that you're happy with,"},{"time":595000,"text":"what people do is they click \"done\""},{"time":597000,"text":"and the markers begin to disappear,"},{"time":599000,"text":"slowly, one by one."},{"time":601000,"text":"It simulates what it is like to invest in something"},{"time":603000,"text":"and to watch that investment pan out."},{"time":606000,"text":"At the end, there will only be one marker left standing"},{"time":609000,"text":"and it will determine our wealth in retirement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":612000,"text":"Yes, this person retired"},{"time":614000,"text":"at 150 percent of their working income in retirement."},{"time":618000,"text":"They're making more money while retired"},{"time":620000,"text":"than they were making while they were working."},{"time":622000,"text":"If you're like most people,"},{"time":624000,"text":"just seeing that gave you a small sense of elation and joy --"},{"time":628000,"text":"just to think about making"},{"time":630000,"text":"50 percent more money in retirement than before."},{"time":633000,"text":"However, had you ended up on the very bottom,"},{"time":635000,"text":"it might have given you a slight sense"},{"time":637000,"text":"of dread and/or nausea"},{"time":639000,"text":"thinking about struggling to get by in retirement."},{"time":643000,"text":"By using this tool over and over"},{"time":645000,"text":"and simulating outcome after outcome,"},{"time":648000,"text":"people can understand"},{"time":650000,"text":"that the investments and savings that they undertake today"},{"time":653000,"text":"determine their well-being in the future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":655000,"text":"Now people are motivated through emotions,"},{"time":658000,"text":"but different people find different things motivating."},{"time":661000,"text":"This is a simulation"},{"time":664000,"text":"that uses graphics,"},{"time":666000,"text":"but other people find motivating what money can buy,"},{"time":668000,"text":"not just numbers."},{"time":670000,"text":"So here I made a distribution builder"},{"time":672000,"text":"where instead of showing numerical outcomes,"},{"time":675000,"text":"I show people what those outcomes will get you,"},{"time":678000,"text":"in particular apartments that you can afford"},{"time":680000,"text":"if you're retiring on 3,000, 2,500,"},{"time":683000,"text":"2,000 dollars per month and so on."},{"time":686000,"text":"As you move down the ladder of apartments,"},{"time":688000,"text":"you see that they get worse and worse."},{"time":691000,"text":"Some of them look like places I lived in as a graduate student."},{"time":695000,"text":"And as you get to the very bottom,"},{"time":699000,"text":"you're faced with the unfortunate reality"},{"time":701000,"text":"that if you don't save anything for retirement,"},{"time":703000,"text":"you won't be able to afford any housing at all."},{"time":706000,"text":"Those are actual pictures of actual apartments"},{"time":708000,"text":"renting for that amount"},{"time":710000,"text":"as advertised on the Internet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":712000,"text":"The last thing I'll show you,"},{"time":714000,"text":"the last behavioral time machine,"},{"time":716000,"text":"is something that I created with Hal Hershfield,"},{"time":719000,"text":"who was introduced to me by my coauthor on a previous project,"},{"time":722000,"text":"Bill Sharpe."},{"time":724000,"text":"And what it is"},{"time":726000,"text":"is an exploration into virtual reality."},{"time":728000,"text":"So what we do is we take pictures of people --"},{"time":731000,"text":"in this case, college-age people --"},{"time":733000,"text":"and we use software to age them"},{"time":735000,"text":"and show these people what they'll look like"},{"time":738000,"text":"when they're 60, 70, 80 years old."},{"time":740000,"text":"And we try to test"},{"time":742000,"text":"whether actually assisting your imagination"},{"time":745000,"text":"by looking at the face of your future self"},{"time":747000,"text":"can change you investment behavior."}]},{"cues":[{"time":749000,"text":"So this is one of our experiments."},{"time":752000,"text":"Here we see the face of the young subject on the left."},{"time":755000,"text":"He's given a control"},{"time":757000,"text":"that allows him to adjust his savings rate."},{"time":759000,"text":"As he moves his savings rate down,"},{"time":761000,"text":"it means that he's saving zero"},{"time":763000,"text":"when it's all the way here at the left."},{"time":765000,"text":"You can see his current annual income --"},{"time":767000,"text":"this is the percentage of his paycheck that he can take home today --"},{"time":770000,"text":"is quite high, 91 percent,"},{"time":772000,"text":"but his retirement income is quite low."},{"time":774000,"text":"He's going to retire on 44 percent"},{"time":776000,"text":"of what he earned while he was working."},{"time":779000,"text":"If he saves the maximum legal amount,"},{"time":782000,"text":"his retirement income goes up,"},{"time":784000,"text":"but he's unhappy"},{"time":786000,"text":"because now he has less money on the left-hand side to spend today."},{"time":790000,"text":"Other conditions show people the future self."},{"time":793000,"text":"And from the future self's point of view, everything is in reverse."},{"time":796000,"text":"If you save very little,"},{"time":798000,"text":"the future self is unhappy"},{"time":800000,"text":"living on 44 percent of the income."},{"time":803000,"text":"Whereas if the present self saves a lot,"},{"time":806000,"text":"the future self is delighted,"},{"time":808000,"text":"where the income is close up near 100 percent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":811000,"text":"To bring this to a wider audience,"},{"time":814000,"text":"I've been working with Hal and Allianz"},{"time":817000,"text":"to create something we call the behavioral time machine,"},{"time":820000,"text":"in which you not only get to see yourself in the future,"},{"time":823000,"text":"but you get to see anticipated emotional reactions"},{"time":826000,"text":"to different levels of retirement wealth."},{"time":829000,"text":"So for instance,"},{"time":831000,"text":"here is somebody using the tool."},{"time":833000,"text":"And just watch the facial expressions"},{"time":835000,"text":"as they move the slider."},{"time":837000,"text":"The younger face gets happier and happier, saving nothing."},{"time":839000,"text":"The older face is miserable."},{"time":841000,"text":"And slowly, slowly we're bringing it up to a moderate savings rate."},{"time":843000,"text":"And then it's a high savings rate."},{"time":845000,"text":"The younger face is getting unhappy."},{"time":847000,"text":"The older face is quite pleased"},{"time":849000,"text":"with the decision."},{"time":852000,"text":"We're going to see if this has an effect on what people do."},{"time":854000,"text":"And what's nice about it"},{"time":856000,"text":"is it's not something that biasing people actually,"},{"time":859000,"text":"because as one face smiles,"},{"time":861000,"text":"the other face frowns."},{"time":863000,"text":"It's not telling you which way to put the slider,"},{"time":865000,"text":"it's just reminding you that you are"},{"time":868000,"text":"connected to and legally tied to"},{"time":870000,"text":"this future self."}]},{"cues":[{"time":872000,"text":"Your decisions today are going to determine its well-being."},{"time":875000,"text":"And that's something that's easy to forget."},{"time":878000,"text":"This use of virtual reality"},{"time":881000,"text":"is not just good for making people look older."},{"time":883000,"text":"There are programs you can get"},{"time":885000,"text":"to see how people might look"},{"time":887000,"text":"if they smoke, if they get too much exposure to the sun,"},{"time":890000,"text":"if they gain weight and so on."},{"time":892000,"text":"And what's good is,"},{"time":894000,"text":"unlike in the experiments that Hal and myself ran with Russ Smith,"},{"time":897000,"text":"you don't have to program these by yourself"},{"time":899000,"text":"in order to see the virtual reality."},{"time":902000,"text":"There are applications you can get on smartphones for just a few dollars"},{"time":905000,"text":"that do the same thing."},{"time":907000,"text":"This is actually a picture of Hal, my coauthor."},{"time":909000,"text":"You might recognize him from the previous demos."},{"time":912000,"text":"And just for kicks we ran his picture"},{"time":915000,"text":"through the balding, aging and weight gain software"},{"time":918000,"text":"to see how he would look."},{"time":920000,"text":"Hal is here, so I think we owe it to him as well as yourself"},{"time":923000,"text":"to disabuse you of that last image."},{"time":927000,"text":"And I'll close it there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":929000,"text":"On behalf of Hal and myself,"},{"time":931000,"text":"I wish all the best to your present and future selves."},{"time":933000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":935000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}